MessagePack.Name: MessagePack
MessagePack.Content: MessagePack is an efficient binary serialization format. I use messagepack to store data on the mod and transmit data over the network.

LiteNetLib.Name: LiteNetLib
LiteNetLib.Content: Lite reliable UDP library for .NET Framework. I use it to provide data transfers between the server/user and I can say that it has performed quite well so far.

Newtonsoft.Name: Newtonsoft
Newtonsoft.Content: Popular high-performance JSON framework for .NET Framework. High Performance? Really? I can't really say I've seen a high performance. I use it in several sections on the mod.

DiscordRichPresence.Name: Discord Rich Presence
DiscordRichPresence.Content: A .NET implementation of Discord's Rich Presence functionality. Very useful, I use it for the game information section in your discord profile.

ExiledPluginArchitecture.Name: Exiled Plugin Architecture
ExiledPluginArchitecture.Content: I quite like Exiled's plugin architecture, and I've created a similar architecture for subnautica, so maybe in the future I can support developers to make plugins to the mod if I want.

CosturaFody.Name: Costura Fody
CosturaFody.Content: Embeds dependencies as resources. This is also very useful. It allows us to combine many dll files into a single exe.
